# Lab Report Design #1

Saved compact professional bilingual layout (Jun 2026). Reference report: `RPT-260623-812322` (~3 pages, 10 tests, 43 rows, 2 microscope images).

## When user requests design 1

Phrases: **تصميم التقرير رقم 1**, **report design 1**, **design #1**, **التصميم رقم 1**

1. Set active PDF generator to design 1: `REPORT_DESIGN=1` (default).
2. Restore files from the frozen snapshot if they were changed:
   - `backend/src/utils/report-designs/design-1.js` → PDF generator (copy logic to active path or wire registry)
   - `frontend/src/utils/report-designs/design-1-print.js` → print iframe CSS
   - `frontend/src/pages/LaboratoryReport.jsx` → HTML structure (title banner, flag legend, patient bar, table)
   - `frontend/src/index.css` → `.lab-rpt-*` screen + print styles
3. Registry: `backend/src/utils/report-designs/index.js` — lists all traits and file paths.
4. Do **not** invent a new layout; match design 1 unless user asks for design 2+.

## Design 1 traits

- Compact A4: patient 4×2 fields, results row 11px, 2-col microscope images (max 120px)
- Y-based PDF pagination (pin `doc.y` after Arabic raster)
- Page footer: report number + `Page N / Total`
- Continuation header + repeating table header on new pages
- Title banner: FINAL/PRELIM badge (brown bar, bilingual title)
- Brand palette `#5B3A29` / `#C9A86A` only for panels
- Flag symbols: ↑ ↓ + − (not long status text)
- Bilingual table headers, QR + confidentiality footer

## Active wiring

- `backend/src/utils/pdf.js` → delegates to `report-designs` registry
- Default design id: **1**
